                  , about the hour of six in the night, on the <rs id="t17901208-14-cd69" type="crimeDate">22d of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17901208-14-off68 t17901208-14-cd69"></join>, with an intent to steal his goods
