               GUILTY
            </rs>, <rs id="t17901208-14-punish73" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17901208-14-punish73" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17901208-14-defend202 t17901208-14-punish73"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>(He was humbly recommended to mercy by the Jury).</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice BULLER.</p>
